	<h3>
	System Requirements
	</h3>
	
	<p>
	<b>Operating Systems:</b> Windows 2000 or higher; Mac OS X (10.1 or higher)
	</p>
	
	<p>
	<b>Display:</b> 1024 x 768 pixel resolution or higher recommended.
	</p>
	
	<p>
	<b>Network Connection:</b> The recommended connection is broadband connection (LAN, DSL, or cable modem). Accessing video content via DSL or a dial-up modem will produce long download times.
	</p>
	
	<p>
	<b>Browsers:</b> Enable Javascript 
	</p>
	
	<p>
	<b>Windows:</b> Best viewed in Firefox 1.0 or later.  Internet Explorer 7, Mozilla,  Netscape 7 or later. 
	</p>
	
	<p>
	<b>Mac OS:</b> Best viewed in Firefox 1.0 or later.  Safari, Netscape 7 or later. 
	</p>
	
	<p>
	<b>Plug-ins:</b> Flash 8 Required 
	</p>
	
